Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reverend Jesse Jackson
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x9zv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Sep 1983
Reverend Jesse Jackson steps into the political spotlight by trying for the Democrat nomination. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less